Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Outcast's Dream!\NHiriluk the Quack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day 3. Prognosis, the\Nbacteria were reduced to 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you'd expect from a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what happens if I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poke, poke...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you become my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really really like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.66,0:02:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in pirates at all.\NAnd I never wanted a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you become my friend,\Nmy other friends will all be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I wanna\Nbecome your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:03:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't insult me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely make\Nyou become my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for you to get\Na healthy smile back,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared an exceptionally\Nnutritious dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though you're still painfully beautiful\Neven after what your body's been through...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lord! When did you use\Nmy kitchen without asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, the roast over there is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's high in protein and is\Ngood for rejuvena-- Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a "madam."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sparkling single...\Nand still youthful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still 139 years old... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's gonna join us\Nand become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, huh? How deep a\Nmeaning that word has to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask without knowing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one man whom he opened\Nup to when he was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man's name was Dr. Hiriluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a quack who gave Chopper\Na name and called him son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We can't find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn quack, Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch him no matter what!\NThose're Wapol-sama's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:05:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes sir!\N--Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go on like this.\NLet's call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There aren't any doctors\Nin this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for the Twenty MDs who\Nbelong exclusively to Wapol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll beg Wapol and call\Nthe Twenty MDs. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll examine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk! N-no thank you!\NPlease don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of people you treated\Nended up getting worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be modest. I just developed a\Nwonderful all-purpose drug yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? It's not what you think.\NThis is a tranquilizer gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use it when the\Npatient's pain is severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm gonna go get the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave!\NIf you want money, I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't take money from sick people.\NI just want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Stop it! I've got a family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Croak! Croak, croak!\NCroak, croak, croak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Croak! Croak!\NCroak, croak! Croak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? This is strange.\NDid I use a wrong ingredient?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought frog extract would work...\NGuess it was a failure. Oh man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry... I didn't\Nmean for this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk! Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold it!\N--Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor hunt has come\Nto the final stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that you and I are the\Nonly doctors left in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol is trying desperately to catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that wasn't the case, you're\Nalready an outcast in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're the worst of the quacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get caught by some doctor hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save this country using\Nmedical science one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't you mean to say\N"destroy the country"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're people on the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you around, quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna see you again,\Nyou thieving doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save as many sick people as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been shot? We need to stop\Nthe bleeding right away or you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a yeti! Shoot him to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made an ointment that even\Nworks on broken bones 3 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?\NYou don't look like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. You're that yeti that\Npeople have been talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't enough! Finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H... How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think... I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never shoot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Dr. Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Chopper and Hiriluk's\Nfirst encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened... to the\Nreindeer taken in by Hiriluk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You can talk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stay quiet for 3 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd hate me if I talked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I talked to humans the\Nother day, they shot me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it's strange for\Na reindeer to speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak, so what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can speak, too...\Na lot better than you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It failed again!\NHey, are you okay, Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Well, you aren't okay\Nto start with, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you calling me Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Tony Tony Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're a reindeer and have\Nfine antlers that could chop down trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a cool name, isn't it?\NThat's what I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Chopper. Always observe patients,\Nand give them proper treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing so will save people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Patients are waiting\Nfor me today once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought lizard eyeballs would work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! It's the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! We'll use the decoy plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got me killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?! You failed to die once already!\NYou clumsy blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me blue nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the first time\NI've fought with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense... To fight,\Nyou have to have an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... is it your first time\Nfor this as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you. It's a gift...\Nas a memento of our making up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gift? Making up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both go through hardships\Nas outcasts, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't hold a grudge against humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is sick right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the citizens and the king\Nsuffer from a sickness of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People would probably say that\Nyou can't treat a sick country,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my invention is complete,\Nthis country will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be a master-thief\Nin a country in the far west.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a serious heart disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to see every possible skilled\Ndoctor and got treated by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but no one was able to cure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being told he'd die,\Nhe passed by a mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while frustrated and unsettled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There... he saw a sight that\Nhe had never seen in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms! He saw vivid\Ncherry blossoms all over the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, he went to see another\Ndoctor and was shocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he was told...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're completely healthy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was cured! It was indeed\Na miracle! Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this was unmistakably medical science!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By being emotionally moved, some sort\Nof change happened in this man's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, there's no disease\Nin this world that can't be cured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says about me,\NI'll save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I raised this skull\Ntowards all the diseases!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a symbol of the belief\Nthat nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By raising this,\NI'll fight just like pirates do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join us and become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Whoa! That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool to be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what are pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are incredible guys at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have large, well-trained\Nbodies and eyes like an eagle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their voices are like\Na thunder splitting the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... really a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.18,0:16:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying, join us!\NIt's fun to be a pirate! Pirates sing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Th-they sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And they dance, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call that being a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!\NAnd they go on lots of adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adventures? So pirates\Ngo on adventures then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Pirates risk their\Nlives to go on adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can meet lots of amazing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool to be a pirate!\NThere're tons of incredible guys at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, go out to sea some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll understand very\Nwell how small your problems are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island that you were born on\Nis like this compared to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's smaller! Like this! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your future lies beyond that sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The good times passed in the\Ntwinkling of an eye... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to bid farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comes for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took one year.\NNow your treatment is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your injuries are\Ncompletely healed, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then... take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.71,0:17:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave! Live as you please!\NI'm busy with my research!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any moral\Nobligation to take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! I'll never cause you\Nany trouble! Please let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll massage your shoulders everyday!\NI'll make you tea and clean the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let me stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any friends!\NI have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, Doctor.\NI'm injured. Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:19:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... to the sea! Go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna... die...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! How many more days do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If you're asking me\Nto examine you, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the money to pay my fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill a person\Nwith a tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you. You'll die at 5 pm\Non the 10th day from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to suffer any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 days... That'll be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 2 days... In 2 days, I'll complete the\Nresearch I've continued for 30 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... make cherry blossoms\Nbloom in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms? So the research\Nyou've continued for 30 years
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was about making cherry blossoms bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The miracle cherry blossoms that\Nsaved you, a master thief, long ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.27,0:20:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fool. This is a winter island\Nwhere it's bitter cold year around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms won't bloom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will! I was a hopeless\Nthug and dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I lived on and was able to\Nhave a profound change of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every human in this world can be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to prove it here in Drum,\Nthe land where I was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. What you're trying to do\Nisn't medical science or any science.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the cherry blossoms bloom,\Nit will do nothing to human bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiriluk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! We're alike. So I will\Nat least teach you before I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there's nothing\Nimpossible in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you can do anything, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the story of these two\Ndoesn't have a happy ending...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...\Nthe miracle cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:22:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy. Are you really\Nlistening to-- Hey, where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I wonder if he's chasing\NTony-kun again... He's refusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to make him join us\Nand become our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's just what you want, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.56,0:23:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... I wonder if there's\Nany medicine that works on fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hiriluk's Cherry Blossoms\NAnd The Will That Gets Carried On!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
